1) 修改 /etc/X11/xorg.conf, 我自己是改成這樣

Section "Screen"
        Identifier      "Default Screen"
        Monitor         "Configured Monitor"
        Device          "Configured Video Device"
        SubSection      "Dispaly"
        Depth           24
        Modes           "1024x768"
        Virtual         2560 2560
        EndSubSection
EndSection

(2) 安裝 grandr 這支程式, 就可以設定延伸桌面囉 ~~~~~~



1. 修改 /etc/X11/xorg.conf

Section "Screen"
        Identifier "Default Screen"
        Monitor "Configured Monitor"
        Device "Configured Video Device"
        SubSection "Dispaly"
        Depth 24
        Modes "1024x768"
        Virtual 2560 2560
        EndSubSection
EndSection

2. 安裝 grandr或 xrandr 這支程式, 就可以設定延伸桌面了。

